      <title>韩国央行誓言在政治动荡中稳定市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/south-korea-s-central-bank-vows-to-stabilize-markets-amid-political-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自韩国立法者投票弹劾总统尹锡烈以来，韩国央行首次发表声明，誓言要稳定金融市场，并强调“不间断实施”关键财政和经济措施的重要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/south-korea-s-central-bank-vows-to-stabilize-markets-amid-political-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国监管机构誓言稳定房地产和股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/china-housing-regulator-sees-stabilization-signs-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在高层领导人会议呼吁加大刺激措施之后，中国监管机构承诺加大力度稳定房地产和股市，并实施更有效的财政政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/china-housing-regulator-sees-stabilization-signs-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 04:06:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走强、特朗普风险影响亚洲投资者 2025 年最佳投资方向</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/strong-dollar-trump-risks-shape-asia-investors-top-2025-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球基金正在探索将新经济与旧经济相融合的方法，以保护其在2025年的亚洲投资免受美国贸易政策不确定性和美元走强的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/strong-dollar-trump-risks-shape-asia-investors-top-2025-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Enbridge 管道公司称威斯康星州漏油事件清理工作正在进行中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/enbridge-pipeline-says-wisconsin-oil-spill-s-cleanup-in-progress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安桥公司 (Enbridge Inc.) 周六表示，11 月 11 日在威斯康星州泄漏的 960 桶石油中已有 60% 被清理干净，受影响的土壤也正在被清除。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/enbridge-pipeline-says-wisconsin-oil-spill-s-cleanup-in-progress</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 23:59:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗德岛社会服务门户网站遭网络犯罪分子入侵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/rhode-island-social-services-portal-breached-by-cybercriminals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗德岛州用于管理公共福利的计算机系统遭到黑客攻击，黑客威胁称，如果不支付费用，他们就会公布个人数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/rhode-island-social-services-portal-breached-by-cybercriminals</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 23:37:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>24 小时降息结束全球央行宽松政策年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/fed-interest-rates-24-hours-of-cuts-that-end-year-of-global-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年是通货膨胀率下降到足以让大多数发达经济体开始放松货币政策的一年，而随着美联储牵头的 24 小时连续决策，这一年即将结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/fed-interest-rates-24-hours-of-cuts-that-end-year-of-global-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏里南称石油特许权使用费支付将改善税收行业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/suriname-says-oil-royalties-payout-will-improve-tax-sector</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏里南财政部长斯坦利·拉戈巴辛 (Stanley Raghoebarsing) 表示，政府将只向在税务系统登记的居民支付石油特许权使用费，以减少未纳税或未受到监管的经济部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/suriname-says-oil-royalties-payout-will-improve-tax-sector</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 20:05:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>写字楼房地产市场崩盘开始在地区性银行浮现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/office-property-meltdown-is-starting-to-surface-at-regional-banks-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[办公楼价值的暴跌对美国银行产生了连锁影响，尤其是小型银行，它们在商业房地产账簿上加大了贷款修改的使用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/office-property-meltdown-is-starting-to-surface-at-regional-banks-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 18:47:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
